{
  "stem": "6762.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all three of us, we talked to the guy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was very nice, [INAUDIBLE], and he gave us some food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We ate.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We talked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then he sent us to work to the collective farm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We collective farm, we worked a few days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know, maybe a couple of weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't-- I can't recall how long-- a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had the misfortune, a scorpion bit me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the farm, we w-- we worked by the grape-- grapes trees.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Grapes was lying like that on the ground.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Grapes, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But what I did-- I know it-- I took a razor blade, and I cut it, and I took out-- sucked out all the stuff from the pain.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I run to the clinic-- the place where I knew there were doctors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I came there, and he says, what did you do?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said to him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, there's nothing else to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You can go back home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I did the right thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I just sucked out the poison, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Put a bandage of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You clean around the trees around the soil and all that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Don't ask.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was there guys.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was one room with bunks, you know, bed bunks like that without any covers, without blankets, just lay in bed bunks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was mighty cold so we-- we found some old furniture and made fire when you heat it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But after a very short time-- excuse me-- I don't remember how long, a few weeks maybe or so-- we were called back to the-- to the police there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this-- this captain there-- whatever he was in the police-- he told us, listen guys, in a couple of days, tomorrow, after tomorrow, you're going to get a paper.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
